import { Container, Row, Col } from 'react-bootstrap'
import Battlefield from './Battlefield'
import PlayerInfo from './PlayerInfo'
import DeckInfo from './DeckInfo'

function GameBoard() {
    return (
        <Container fluid >
            <Row>
            <Col xs={5}>
                <PlayerInfo/>
            </Col>
            <Col xs={5}></Col>
                <Battlefield/>
                <DeckInfo/>
            </Row>
        </Container>
    )
}

export default GameBoard;
